column2: SELECT TOP # s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z,   k.petroRad_r,k.expAB_r,  g.bpt,g.sigmaStars,g.sigmaStarsErr,  z.spiral,z.elliptical,z.uncertain,m.mstellar_median,m.mstellar_err FROM PhotoTag as p  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll k ON p.objid = k.objID  JOIN emissionLinesPort g ON s.specobjID = g.specobjID  JOIN zooSpec z ON p.objid = z.objid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# m ON s.specobjID = m.specobjID WHERE s.class = &&& AND zWarning = # AND s.z<#
